6 position snapshot

Plot of the last four positions for all the tags which have generated an argos position within the last 3 days

7 plot pressure sensors

PROVISIONAL plot status cutoffs and bat voltage. Cutoffs are in dotted red lines. These are either:

  1. healthy tags: the last status messages as a conservative cutoff and on tags that are still actively transmitting this is likely to increase
  2. unhealthy pressure transducer tags: if there are 2 status messages (crcd) where the | zerodepth | > 10 then this is the last good status message before the 1st of those two bad messages.

We have settled on a more complicated cutoff system to capture a little more very likely good data for BRS (ask wrc for details). But this gives you a general idea of approx. cutoffs and pressure transducer health.
